  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "859921_4_695-741",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "695-741",
      "markText": "因为这个国家对自身文化太过骄傲，所以其子孙似乎无法迅速认识到改变的必要性，以应对欧洲的挑战。",
      "totalCount": 3600,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=859921&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=695&rangeEnd=741",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c8325e05d1f110c8edf190?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=695&rangeEnd=741"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "859921_6_765-804",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "765-804",
      "markText": "不管中国传统农民多么值得称颂，历史学家对老百姓的欣赏，仍旧只能停留在情感层面。",
      "totalCount": 1984,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=859921&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=765&rangeEnd=804",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c8325e05d1f110c8edf190?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=765&rangeEnd=804"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "859921_6_1158-1203",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1158-1203",
      "markText": "这些被理想化的农民勤劳节俭，不畏劳作的艰辛，乐于缴纳赋税，以回报统治阶级所谓的家长式关爱。",
      "totalCount": 1344,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=859921&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1158&rangeEnd=1203",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c8325e05d1f110c8edf190?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1158&rangeEnd=1203"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "859921_6_5848-5880",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "5848-5880",
      "markText": "在1877至1878年的艰难岁月里，中国华北足足饿死了一千万人。",
      "totalCount": 1209,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=859921&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5848&rangeEnd=5880",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c8325e05d1f110c8edf190?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5848&rangeEnd=5880"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "859921_6_1400-1443",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1400-1443",
      "markText": "尽管几乎没有任何叛军首领真正夺取政权，但他们领导的那些运动，却预示着新的朝代即将到来。",
      "totalCount": 1162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=859921&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1400&rangeEnd=1443",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c8325e05d1f110c8edf190?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1400&rangeEnd=1443"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "859921_6_5363-5401",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "5363-5401",
      "markText": "1940年，华北农业经济之所以陷入危机，都是因为技术落后，而非财富分配不均。",
      "totalCount": 1157,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=859921&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5363&rangeEnd=5401",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c8325e05d1f110c8edf190?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5363&rangeEnd=5401"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "859921_6_883-913",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "883-913",
      "markText": "直到近代，他们才拥有了属于自己的政治权利，并学会为自己说话。",
      "totalCount": 1136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=859921&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=883&rangeEnd=913",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c8325e05d1f110c8edf190?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=883&rangeEnd=913"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "859921_10_4367-4442",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "4367-4442",
      "markText": "如此一来，商人们满足于按市场机制调整价格所带来的丰厚利润，根本没有提升技术的意识。因此，中国的商人或许能跻身世界一流商人的行列，却永远成不了大资本家。",
      "totalCount": 1134,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=859921&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4367&rangeEnd=4442",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c8325e05d1f110c8edf190?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4367&rangeEnd=4442"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "859921_10_3762-3804",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "3762-3804",
      "markText": "中国没能出现类似萨克森纺车或飞梭之类的发明，或许是原材料有限，而劳动力却过剩的缘故。",
      "totalCount": 1116,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=859921&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=3762&rangeEnd=3804",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c8325e05d1f110c8edf190?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=3762&rangeEnd=3804"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "859921_6_1854-1912",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1854-1912",
      "markText": "到19世纪，国民经济已经举步维艰。毫无疑问，导致这一局面的原因，要归结于几个世纪以来，中国农民不断带来的非暴力改变。",
      "totalCount": 900,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=859921&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1854&rangeEnd=1912",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c8325e05d1f110c8edf190?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1854&rangeEnd=1912"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "859921_10_13762-13818",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "13762-13818",
      "markText": "正如商人，无论多么富有，都会渴望跻身士绅之列。文人亦是如此，无论多么锐意创新，也希望有朝一日能在京城为皇帝效命。",
      "totalCount": 832,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=859921&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=13762&rangeEnd=13818",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c8325e05d1f110c8edf190?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=13762&rangeEnd=13818"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "859921_10_6690-6724",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "6690-6724",
      "markText": "儒家一贯的政治思想也更强调士大夫的道德操守，而非制度上的监督和平衡。",
      "totalCount": 826,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=859921&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=6690&rangeEnd=6724",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c8325e05d1f110c8edf190?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=6690&rangeEnd=6724"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "859921_6_3997-4189",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3997-4189",
      "markText": "农学家们并未改良设备，而是通过增加家庭劳动力的投入，来达到增产的目的。于是，增产靠的便是农民个人的体力。",
      "totalCount": 810,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=859921&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3997&rangeEnd=4189",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c8325e05d1f110c8edf190?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3997&rangeEnd=4189"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "859921_8_2656-2707",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2656-2707",
      "markText": "中央政府通过控制科举考试的内容、考试频率和考试难度，来达到控制这群精英的意识形态、才能及其规模的目的。",
      "totalCount": 792,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=859921&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2656&rangeEnd=2707",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c8325e05d1f110c8edf190?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2656&rangeEnd=2707"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "859921_8_4647-4682",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "4647-4682",
      "markText": "成功的可能性既不能缓解社会不满情绪，也无法给予这个文明持续发展的动力。",
      "totalCount": 736,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=859921&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4647&rangeEnd=4682",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c8325e05d1f110c8edf190?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4647&rangeEnd=4682"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "859921_10_11161-11223",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "11161-11223",
      "markText": "商人既然可以如此轻易地进入精英阶层，他们就没有推翻儒家等级制度的动力，也没有联合其他资产阶级同业，共同提高其社会地位的志向。",
      "totalCount": 702,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=859921&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=11161&rangeEnd=11223",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c8325e05d1f110c8edf190?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=11161&rangeEnd=11223"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "859921_4_632-674",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "632-674",
      "markText": "所以，我们对抵制欧洲征服的一些更古老文明的看法，因西方全球扩张带来的新视野而扭曲了。",
      "totalCount": 675,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=859921&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=632&rangeEnd=674",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c8325e05d1f110c8edf190?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=632&rangeEnd=674"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "859921_4_801-826",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "801-826",
      "markText": "既然渐进的改革无法进行，横扫一切的革命就势在必行。",
      "totalCount": 672,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=859921&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=801&rangeEnd=826",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c8325e05d1f110c8edf190?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=801&rangeEnd=826"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "859921_12_11160-11230",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "11160-11230",
      "markText": "朕自登极十七载，上干天咎，逆贼直逼京师。诸臣误朕也。朕无颜见先皇于地下，将发覆面，任贼分裂朕尸。可将文臣尽行杀死，勿坏陵寝，勿伤我百姓一人。",
      "totalCount": 646,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=859921&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=11160&rangeEnd=11230",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c8325e05d1f110c8edf190?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=11160&rangeEnd=11230"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "859921_4_859-939",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "859-939",
      "markText": "由于没能力进行根本性的内部变革，中国将不得不被外部势力推向革命。但如果这个解释是正确的，那就必须假设：未受干扰的中国会无限重复它过去的历史，固守传统、一成不变。",
      "totalCount": 640,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=859921&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=859&rangeEnd=939",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0c8325e05d1f110c8edf190?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=859&rangeEnd=939"
    }
